"src/sim/README"

This is the root directory for all simulation-related functions, 
subprograms and objects.

Contents:

prsim/ -- basic production rule simulator, based largely on older
	cflat-based version, but with improvements and new features.

chpsim/ -- CHP mixed-level simulator, integrating PRS and CHP in a 
	single event-driven simulator.  

TODO:

sprsim/ -- sizing-based PRS-simulator

